{
  "page": "Elinda Massey",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Massey\" title=\"House Massey\"><img alt=\"House Massey.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/06/House_Massey.svg/50px-House_Massey.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/06/House_Massey.svg/75px-House_Massey.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/06/House_Massey.svg/100px-House_Massey.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Elinda Massey</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Massey\" title=\"House Massey\"><img alt=\"House Massey.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/06/House_Massey.svg/50px-House_Massey.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/06/House_Massey.svg/75px-House_Massey.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/06/House_Massey.svg/100px-House_Massey.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lady-in-waiting\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lady-in-waiting\">Lady-in-waiting</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Massey\" title=\"House Massey\">House Massey</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Blacks\" title=\"Blacks\">Blacks</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Crownlands\" title=\"Crownlands\">Crownlands</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_and_Blood\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Fire and Blood\">Fire and Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">Played by</span></th><td>\nJordon Stevens</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">TV series</span></th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/House_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"House of the Dragon\">House of the Dragon</a></i>: <a href=\"/index.php/House_of_the_Dragon_-_Season_1\" title=\"House of the Dragon - Season 1\">Season 1</a> | <a href=\"/index.php/House_of_the_Dragon_-_Season_2\" title=\"House of the Dragon - Season 2\">2</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Elinda Massey</b> was a noblewoman of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Massey\" title=\"House Massey\">House Massey</a> and a <a href=\"/index.php/Lady-in-waiting\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lady-in-waiting\">lady-in-waiting</a> to Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaenyra_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaenyra Targaryen\">Rhaenyra Targaryen</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>In the television adaptation <i><a href=\"/index.php/House_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"House of the Dragon\">House of the Dragon</a></i>, Elinda is portrayed by Jordon Stevens.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#House_of_the_Dragon\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">House of the Dragon</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character\">Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Elinda_Massey&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Elinda was the youngest and the gentlest of Rhaenyra's ladies-in-waiting.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Elinda_Massey&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Elinda Massey was among the four <a href=\"/index.php/Lady-in-waiting\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lady-in-waiting\">ladies-in-waiting</a> who accompanied Rhaenyra during her <a href=\"/index.php/Flight_to_Dragonstone\" title=\"Flight to Dragonstone\">flight</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone\" title=\"Dragonstone\">Dragonstone</a>. Supposedly she gouged out her own eyes at the sight of her queen being devoured by the <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">dragon</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Sunfyre\" title=\"Sunfyre\">Sunfyre</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>After Rhaenyra's death, Elinda and the three other ladies-in-waiting were put in cells in <a href=\"/index.php/Sea_Dragon_Tower\" title=\"Sea Dragon Tower\">Sea Dragon Tower</a> to await ransom.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"House_of_the_Dragon\">House of the Dragon</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Elinda_Massey&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: House of the Dragon\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>In the television series <i><a href=\"/index.php/House_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"House of the Dragon\">House of the Dragon</a></i>, it is specified that Elinda is the daughter of <a href=\"/index.php/Gormon_Massey\" title=\"Gormon Massey\">Gormon Massey</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Stonedance\" title=\"Lord of Stonedance\">Lord of Stonedance</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Elinda_Massey&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Dying of the Dragons - Rhaenyra Overthrown.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Warner Bros. Discovery: <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://press.wbd.com/us/bio/house-dragon-s2-character-descriptions\">HOTD Season 2 Character descriptions</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404081127\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.073 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.258 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 756/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10578/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 7357/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1468/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nU